properties.Name: EquifaxCompanyBusinessLevels
properties.Description:
Provide EFX IDs and additional identifying information on the business levels in the family tree which have ultimate financial responsibility for the inquired site. 

Up to five EFX IDs for each business are returned: inquired site, headquarters
site, immediate parent, ultimate domestic and ultimate global parent.

Columns.Name: EfxId
Columns.Description: The EFX ID™ is a unique and persistent nine-digit number that identifies and tracks the business unit with which you have the credit relationship;

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description:
Provides the timestamp when the inquiry was made as recorded
by Equifax (Eastern Time).

Columns.Name: EquifaxBusinessLevelTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Business Level Type.
